          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/516-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Stir&nbsp;the <strong>wholegrain mustard</strong> and half <span class=\"text-danger\">[all]&nbsp;</span>the <strong>cr&egrave;me fra&icirc;che</strong> into the cooked chicken and cook for a further min until just warmed through</p>\r\n<p>Once warmed, remove from the heat and stir in the remaining <strong>tarragon</strong></p>\r\n<p>Taste for seasoning, adding <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> if needed</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
